<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Page non trouvée - 404</title>
    <style>
        body { background: #f7f8fa; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
        .notfound-container { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(30,40,90,0.10); padding: 2.5rem 2.5rem 2rem 2.5rem; max-width: 410px; width: 100%; text-align: center; }
        .notfound-title { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; color: #1a2340; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .notfound-msg { color: #555; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .notfound-link a { color: #274080; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
        .notfound-link a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="notfound-container">
        <div class="notfound-title">404 - Page non trouvée</div>
        <div class="notfound-msg">La page que vous cherchez n'existe pas ou a été déplacée.</div>
        <div class="notfound-link"><a href="/exemple/backend-mvc/public/login">Retour à l'accueil</a></div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
